  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Certain lung disease medications can influence diagnostic tests and research investigations.
      This study will investigate how long ipratropium bromide must be withheld before a
      methacholine challenge test can be conducted. This information will be useful for validating
      current guidelines.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
